    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127730/extras/c7d51c41ca24475608dfeb9a46af4b33.avif?t=1749682268\" width=610 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 加入解放阿尔丁王国(Aldin)的战役！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投身数十小时的战略对决，扭转战局，亲手改写反抗军的命运！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127730/extras/760f97533e52be0de46095c9b908006e.poster.avif?t=1749682268\" width=610 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127730/extras/760f97533e52be0de46095c9b908006e.webm?t=1749682268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 释放&quot;爆发技&quot;(Burst Techs)强化战力！把握时机发动，一举扭转战局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 运筹帷幄，掌控敌我站位！抢占战术要地，主宰战场节奏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127730/extras/53e4cd94e67848a17cb86a773c6517eb.poster.avif?t=1749682268\" width=610 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127730/extras/53e4cd94e67848a17cb86a773c6517eb.webm?t=1749682268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 探索多样地图，采集资源，在JRPG式的自由漫游模式中体验丰富事件！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 邂逅各色NPC，进行交易，并展开激动人心的任务旅程！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127730/extras/9880b2de42e1a189c8623b094612124a.poster.avif?t=1749682268\" width=610 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127730/extras/9880b2de42e1a189c8623b094612124a.webm?t=1749682268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 体验跌宕起伏的角色故事线，经营错综复杂的人物关系，做出关键抉择——亲手铸就反抗军的未来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 自由组建战队，定制专属技能组合，通过职业搭配突破多样胜利条件！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 40+职业任选，千变万化技能组合，打造属于你的无限战术流派！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127730/extras/51484ff241f4f411412dfcce7437275b.poster.avif?t=1749682268\" width=610 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127730/extras/51484ff241f4f411412dfcce7437275b.webm?t=1749682268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 穿越多样地域——每张地图独有的环境机制，考验你的临场应变力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 在「回归者」营地中统筹资源与升级：强化部队战力，支援盟友势力，扩张你的影响力！</p>",
